author: hwright
msg: Because Ev2 doesn't deal in deltas, the Ev2 replay implementation doesn't need
bother with a flag to request them.
If callers what deltas, it is there responsibility for computing them.
(svn_repos_replay2): Ignore the send_deltas flag when calling the Ev2 version.
(replay_node): Don't take a source_root, since we don't need it.
